name.jp: ロー アップカット ストーン

description.en: A Magic Stone that increases your Attack Power (ATK) by 10%. Lasts 1 Hour. If you listen closely, you can hear it humming slightly.
description.ar: A Magic Stone that increases your Attack Power (ATK) by 10%. Lasts 1 Hour. If you listen closely, you can hear it humming slightly.
description.br: Uma Pedra Mágica que acrescenta +10% de Ataque por 60 minutos. Se você escutar atentamente, poderá ouvi-la zumbindo levemente.
description.de: Ein magischer Stein, der deine Angriffskraft (ATK) um 10% erhöht. Hält 1 Stunde. Wenn du genau hinhörst, kannst du ihn leicht summen hören.
